Je l'?

1136
01:15:15,200 --> 01:15:17,320
Odlicno, Heder.

1137
01:15:17,570 --> 01:15:19,990
Bravo, tu je.
Ucini mi uslugu.

1138
01:15:20,110 --> 01:15:24,860
