1261
01:23:11,500 --> 01:23:12,790
Džejn i Carli.

1262
01:23:23,000 --> 01:23:25,580
Gospodine, pocinjemo sa službom.

1263
01:23:26,000 --> 01:23:27,330
Pocnite.

