01:23:35,290 --> 01:23:36,450
Gdine Koen?

1265
01:23:37,660 --> 01:23:38,790
Necete da udjete?

1266
01:23:39,660 --> 01:23:40,450
Žao mi je.

1267
01:23:41,330 --> 01:23:42,000
Mislio sam da mogu...

1268
01:23:42,160 --> 01:23:45,250
